#menu
.site-options.l-container
  .banner.l-banner
    h1 Just Right Sites
    p
      | Cluttered sites drown content. clov3r is Agile by building only the amount of site you need.
      br
      | Agile prevents spending time and money on features you never use.
      br
      | Let's build only what you need.
  ul.bullets
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'whale.gif'
      .bullet-content
        h2 Splash Page
        p This is square one. A single page to show who you are and some other information like a bio, services, and contact details.
        p= link_to 'view details', '/products/splash-page'
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'page.gif'
      .bullet-content
        h2 + Page
        p Once you have more content than can fit on the splash page, add pages for organization.
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'blog.png'
      .bullet-content
        h2 Basic Blog
        p Blogs are similar to Pages but with additional features like an over list of posts, tags for sorting, and comments for reader feedback.
  ul.bullets
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'support.png'
      .bullet-content
        h2 Setup stuff
        p If terms like 'CNAME', 'DNS', and 'GoDaddy' make you shudder, then I can help register your domain name as well get you setup with an email account.
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'gallery.png'
      .bullet-content
        h2 Photo Albums
        p Splash pages should hold about 12 - 15 photos. After you have more then it's probably time to organize photos by albums.
    li.bullet.three-col-bullet
      .bullet-image= image_tag 'flair.png'
      .bullet-content
        h2 Flare
        p Flare are the additional items that make your site more personable. These features should only be added when needed.

